&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.1; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.1; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Crooked is hiring an &lt;strong&gt;Account Executive, Brand, Social &amp;amp; Live Sales Partnerships&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;on the &lt;strong&gt;Sales team &lt;/strong&gt;reporting to the &lt;strong&gt;VP of Sales.&lt;/strong&gt; This role will focus on developing and closing high-impact partnerships with brands seeking cultural relevance, large-scale audience reach, and integrated storytelling opportunities across Crooked’s podcasts, simulcast video, social platforms, newsletters, and live events. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This position will lead direct sales efforts with brand marketers and agencies focused on brand awareness, cultural moments, branded storytelling, social content and live experiences. The role will also help develop premium sponsorship opportunities tied to Crooked content and its tentpole events including Crooked Con, live tour programming, and special event coverage such as the White House Correspondents’ Dinner.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.1; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate will have deep relationships with holding company, brand, and agency decision makers, experience selling integrated media partnerships, and a track record of closing large multi-platform deals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.1; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Crooked has adopted a hybrid work model for our entire staff. We believe that the best work is done in a hybrid capacity as it combines the flexibility of working from home with in-person collaboration. However, some positions at Crooked are remote for specific strategic reasons. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;And for this role, it is based in New York with some travel required. We are ideally looking for New York based candidates or individuals are willing to relocate before their start date.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
